{"tid":1942276,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳富豪酒店分階段炒200人","createTime":"2020-03-25T03:30:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T04:16:42.000Z","uid":10540,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5219ad65aa1652681b77b1078242334b589f38a5","tid":1942276,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20200325/photo/0325-00176-030b1.jpg?t=1585107038473\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200325%2Fphoto%2F0325-00176-030b1.jpg%3Ft%3D1585107038473&h=f583d1c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n疫情持續令訪港旅客暴跌，酒店業自然首當其衝。酒店工會主席徐考澧表示，近兩個月最少有五百名酒店業員工被裁，<span style=\"color: red;\">又指據其所知富豪酒店集團亦會分階段裁減約二百人，昨率先裁減富豪機場酒店四十名員工</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外，目前有十五至二十間酒店表明會接待需要隔離的人士，但有酒店員工反映防護衣物及口罩數量不足，亦未知酒店設施是否符合接待相關人士，部分更寧願離職以免染疫。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>市民爆料 富豪機場酒店裁減40人</strong><br />\n有市民向本報報料，指富豪機場酒店昨裁減四十人。富豪酒店集團回應指，沒有進一步資料提供。<br />\n<br />\n該集團早於上月確認裁員消息，解釋自去年下半年起，酒店業已面對各種困難和挑戰，加上新冠肺炎，進一步打擊香港酒店業務，嚴重威脅酒店業的營運，該集團必須採取應對措施，包括調整人手部署，以維持有效率的營運。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20200325/00176_030.html?fbclid=IwAR1e7X6siBrNMD-WrYV-ij_tNRCCfCk7mHCeGa5cdyc4BWUvjKSPGPhUmco\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200325%2F00176_030.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1e7X6siBrNMD-WrYV-ij_tNRCCfCk7mHCeGa5cdyc4BWUvjKSPGPhUmco&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2BynyWHaP8IcnP89ZPrefCyuoo%3D&h=3af54ab6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20200325/00176_030.html?fbclid=IwAR1e7X6siBrNMD-WrYV-ij_tNRCCfCk7mHCeGa5cdyc4BWUvjKSPGPhUmco</a>"},{"pid":"2d76b86cf78e1b8ff081b15b15fcd89de7db06ae","tid":1942276,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:32:18.000Z","msg":"369"},{"pid":"6e140b462cacfc49fc076c76a4b7b081b33eceea","tid":1942276,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T04:1